      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dents consistent with its age, and the interior shows clear signs of wear, including some staining on the upholstery and minor cracking on the dashboard. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may require some routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads and a tune-up. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that has been used regularly but is starting to show its age both inside and out.",
