      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that still has plenty of life left? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got some miles under its belt, but it runs beautifully and is ready for its next adventure with you. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 29500.0,
