      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a purist\u2019s configuration featuring the S54B32 high-revving inline-six. This engine utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver a sharp, linear throttle response all the way to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and predictable power delivery. Crucial preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precision of the M-tuned geometry. This is a driver-focused example that balances mechanical excellence with the honest character of a well-maintained performance machine.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
